America's Army deploys to Palisav Island in enemy Czervenian territory. Captain Carl Reed and his Quick Reaction Force are sent to capture a high value clan leader at a secret Red Coin terrorist training camp, and it's a risky mission. Everyone believes a mole within the Coalition is leaking information to Red Coin, and Commander Belova, the local Police Chief, is at the top of the list of Reed's suspects. When Red Coin fighters ambush the team armed with advanced Czervenian hardware, the team must fight together to escape the forests of Palisav alive in America's Army #5 - Tipping Point.
